{"word":"H7286 - רָדַד - râdad - raw-dad' - Spend","slug":"H7286","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">רָדַד</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>râdad"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>raw-dad'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Spend"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E8;&#x05D3;&#x05D3; - ra&#x0302;dad</b> - <i>raw-dad'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>tread</i> in pieces, that is, (figuratively) to <i>conquer</i>, or (specifically) to <i>overlay: - </i>spend, spread, subdue."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7288\">H7288</a>, <a href=\"#/H7289\">H7289</a>"}]}